Package: rollinglda
Type: Package
Title: Construct Consistent Time Series from Textual Data
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2021-08-05
Authors@R: person("Jonas", "Rieger", email="jonas.rieger@tu-dortmund.de", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0007-4478"))
Description: RollingLDA is a rolling version of the Latent Dirichlet Allocation. By an sequential approach, it enables the construction of LDA-based time series of topics that are consistent with previous states of LDA models. After an initial modeling, updates can be computed efficiently, allowing for real-time monitoring and detection of events or structural breaks.
URL: https://github.com/JonasRieger/rollinglda
BugReports: https://github.com/JonasRieger/rollinglda/issues
